 2013-03522013-03-28,  ,  ,  IC, 
ActCanadian Space Agency Act
SubjectCanada-Ontario Agreement on Geospatial Data Exchange
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Industry to enter into an AGREEMENT with Ontario in order to allow the Canadian Space Agency to become a member of the ONTARIO GEOSPATIAL DATA EXCHANGE in order to gain free access to the digital geographic data of Ontario required to implement the Canadian Space Agency‘s Stratospheric Balloon Initiative.
